@*
    CUSTOMER DELETE CONFIRMATION VIEW
    =================================
    
    Veilige klant verwijdering interface met comprehensive customer review.
    Implementeert destructive operation best practices specifiek voor
    customer relationship management.
    
    ARCHITECTUUR:  
    - Strongly-typed Customer model voor complete data access
    - Two-step confirmation pattern voor veiligheid
    - Read-only customer information display
    - Form-based secure deletion
    
    BUSINESS CONTEXT:
    - Customer deletion heeft CRM implications
    - Potential impact op order history
    - GDPR compliance considerations
    - Data retention policy adherence
    
    EDUCATIEVE ASPECTEN:
    - DisplayNameFor voor automatic label generation
    - DisplayFor voor type-safe data rendering
    - Destructive operation UI patterns
    - Definition list semantic structure
    - Form-based secure operations
    
    UI/UX PATTERNS:
    - Clear confirmation question
    - Complete customer data visibility
    - Danger-themed delete button
    - Safe escape route via cancel
    - Consistent Matrix branding
    
    SECURITY & COMPLIANCE:
    - Hidden ID field voor secure identification
    - Two-step confirmation process
    - Complete audit trail capability
    - User verification requirements
*@

@model DataAccessLayer.Models.Customer

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Klant verwijderen";
}

@* HOOFDTITEL: Duidelijke waarschuwing voor destructive operation *@
<h1 class="text-white">Klant verwijderen</h1>

@* MATRIX BRANDING: Consistente achtergrondvideo *@
<video autoplay loop muted playsinline id="bg-video">
    <source src="/Videos/matrix.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    Your browser does not support the video tag.
</video>

@* 
CUSTOMER CONFIRMATION INTERFACE
==============================

Card-based layout voor structured information presentation:
- Matrix-branded styling voor consistency
- Clear warning message voor user awareness
- Complete customer data voor verification
*@
<div class="card matrix-card shadow mb-4">
    @* CONFIRMATION VRAAG: Prominent warning voor destructive action *@
    <h3>Weet u zeker dat u deze klant wilt verwijderen?</h3>
    <div>
        <hr />
        @* 
        CUSTOMER DATA REVIEW
        ===================
        
        Definition list met automatic label generation:
        - DisplayNameFor gebruikt model metadata voor labels
        - DisplayFor voor type-safe data rendering
        - Semantic HTML structure voor accessibility
        *@
        <dl class="row">
            @* CUSTOMER NAME: Primaire identificatie *@
            <dt class = "col-sm-2">
                @Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.Name)
            </dt>
            <dd class = "col-sm-10">
                @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.Name)
            </dd>
            
            @* CUSTOMER ADDRESS: Contact information *@
            <dt class = "col-sm-2">
                @Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.Address)
            </dt>
            <dd class = "col-sm-10">
                @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.Address)
            </dd>
            
            @* CUSTOMER STATUS: Active/inactive indication *@
            <dt class = "col-sm-2">
                @Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.Active)
            </dt>
            <dd class = "col-sm-10">
                @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.Active)
            </dd>
        </dl>
    </div>
}

@* 
DELETE CONFIRMATION ACTIONS
===========================

Two-step delete process voor secure customer removal:
- Form-based submission voor proper HTTP verb usage
- Hidden ID field voor secure customer identification
- Clear action buttons met appropriate styling
*@
<div>
    @* 
    DELETE FORM:
    - asp-action="Delete" routes naar DELETE HTTP method
    - Hidden ID field beschermt tegen URL manipulation
    - Submit triggers final delete confirmation
    *@
    <form asp-action="Delete">
        @* SECURITY: Hidden field voor customer ID protection *@
        <input type="hidden" asp-for="Id" />
        
        @* DESTRUCTIVE ACTION: btn-danger styling voor visual warning *@
        <input type="submit" value="Verwijderen" class="btn btn-danger" /> |
        
        @* ESCAPE ROUTE: Safe return naar customer overview *@
        <a asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-secondary">Terug naar Klantenoverzicht</a>
    </form>
</div>